;= 3 x 128 bytes = 384 bytes, read/written alongside CBBLOCK1 by READCB.     =
;= On disk: output conv (128B) + input conv (128B) + semigraphic map (128B).  =
;= Values below are residual .COM file data, overwritten by READCB at runtime.=
;==============================================================================
